<Input>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal"></Text-field>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal">Integrate the system and create a Poincare map</Text-field>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal"></Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L535" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">xdot := (x, y, u, v) -&gt; u:</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">ydot := (x, y, u, v) -&gt; v:</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">udot := (x, y, u, v) -&gt;  2*v + x - mu1*(x+mu2)/s1(x,y)^3 - mu2*(x-mu1)/s2(x,y)^3:</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">vdot := (x, y, u, v) -&gt; -2*u + y - mu1*y/s1(x,y)^3       - mu2*y/s2(x,y)^3:</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle7" alignment="left" firstindent="0" spacebelow="0" linebreak="space" rightmargin="0" bulletsuffix="" pagebreak-before="false" leftmargin="0" linespacing="0.0" initial="0" layout_style_name="_pstyle7" spaceabove="0" bullet="none">DE1 := diff(x(t),t) = xdot(x(t),y(t),u(t),v(t)):</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle7" alignment="left" firstindent="0" spacebelow="0" linebreak="space" rightmargin="0" bulletsuffix="" pagebreak-before="false" leftmargin="0" linespacing="0.0" initial="0" layout_style_name="_pstyle7" spaceabove="0" bullet="none">DE2 := diff(y(t),t) = ydot(x(t),y(t),u(t),v(t)):</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle7" alignment="left" firstindent="0" spacebelow="0" linebreak="space" rightmargin="0" bulletsuffix="" pagebreak-before="false" leftmargin="0" linespacing="0.0" initial="0" layout_style_name="_pstyle7" spaceabove="0" bullet="none">DE3 := diff(u(t),t) = udot(x(t),y(t),u(t),v(t)):</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">DE4 := diff(v(t),t) = vdot(x(t),y(t),u(t),v(t)):</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle7" alignment="left" firstindent="0" spacebelow="0" linebreak="space" rightmargin="0" bulletsuffix="" pagebreak-before="false" leftmargin="0" linespacing="0.0" initial="0" layout_style_name="_pstyle7" spaceabove="0" bullet="none">DE := DE1, DE2, DE3, DE4;</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
